OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773306338
OL,3,CPrimary school in Kent to receive #1.2
OL,4,Cmillion in funding for expansion plans
OL,6,FA primary school in Kent will receive
OL,7,F#1.2 million in funding as the council
OL,8,Fplans to expand the school.
OL,10,FKent County Council (KCC) says the
OL,11,Fmoney will be used to build three new
OL,12,Fclassrooms at Ebbsfleet Green Primary
OL,13,FSchool.
OL,15,FIt said the need for extra capacity
OL,16,Fhas been driven by rapid growth across
OL,17,Fthe Swanscombe and Ebbsfleet area and
OL,18,Fdelays to the opening of a new primary
OL,19,Fprovision elsewhere.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
