PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773306338
OL,3,CPrimary school in Kent to receive #1.2
OL,4,Cmillion in funding for expansion plans
OL,6,FEbbsfleet Green Primary School and
OL,7,FMaritime Academy Trust previously
OL,8,Fagreed to temporarily increase their
OL,9,FReception intake from 60 to 90 pupils
OL,10,Fover two years, in September 2024 and
OL,11,FSeptember 2025.
OL,13,FThe school opened in 2020 and was
OL,14,Finitially able to house the larger
OL,15,F"bulge" classes in spare classrooms
OL,16,Fthat were not being used.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773306338
OL,3,CPrimary school in Kent to receive #1.2
OL,4,Cmillion in funding for expansion plans
OL,6,FHowever, the council says the school
OL,7,Fis due to reach full capacity by
OL,8,FSeptember 2027 and the expansion will
OL,9,Fmake space for the larger "bulge"
OL,10,Fclasses to continue their education on
OL,11,Fsite safely and comfortably.
OL,13,FThe school is home to The Woodlands, a
OL,14,F15place Specialist Resource Provision
OL,15,Ffor pupils with autism spectrum
OL,16,Fdisorder.
OL,18,FIn the longer term, once the "bulge"
OL,19,Fyear groups move through the school,
OL,20,Fthe new classrooms could be used as
OL,21,Fadditional SEND intervention spaces.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773306338
OL,3,CPrimary school in Kent to receive #1.2
OL,4,Cmillion in funding for expansion plans
OL,6,FBeverley Fordham, KCC's Cabinet Member
OL,7,Ffor Education and Skills, said: "The
OL,8,Fexpansion represents a significant
OL,9,Fstep in ensuring children across the
OL,10,FSwanscombe and Ebbsfleet area can
OL,11,Fcontinue to access highquality,
OL,12,Finclusive education close to home now
OL,13,Fand for years to come.
OL,15,F"I am particularly pleased that this
OL,16,Fexpansion will also support our
OL,17,Flongterm plans to strengthen SEND
OL,18,Fprovision, ensuring that children with
OL,19,Fthe most complex needs can access the
OL,20,Fright support close to home."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
