PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773306338
OL,3,CPrimary school in Kent to receive #1.2
OL,4,Cmillion in funding for expansion plans
OL,6,FJoshua Croucher, Head of School at
OL,7,FEbbsfleet Green Primary School, added:
OL,8,F" We are proud to support our local
OL,9,Fcommunity's rapid growth.
OL,11,F"By partnering with KCC to increase
OL,12,Four intake, we created significantly
OL,13,Fmore places for local families to
OL,14,Faccess a school close to home.
OL,16,F"This investment and the new
OL,17,Fclassrooms allow us to maintain high
OL,18,Fstandards for our current pupils while
OL,19,Fopening up vital new early years
OL,20,Fopportunities to meet the growing
OL,21,Fneeds in the local area."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
